data.name: infoBox.Text
data.value:
!Welcome to Riptide!
Rules: 1) placing ships: - you can select ship type in the combobox above the left field, - click on the left field to set the start of the ship, - double click on the left of the field to set the end of the ship, - if it's a boat, then just doubleclick on the left field; 2) press ready button to connect to a player; 3) each player takes turnes until all of player's ships are destroyed.
This programm was created by Dudkin Nikita.
